{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "第十一回\"太湖男儿\"讲述展梦白被萧飞雨强行带离桃林，乘船渡太湖时遭遇方辛父子暗算。方氏父子藏身底舱，意图用闷香迷晕二人逼问白布旗下落，却被展梦白察觉异样。萧飞雨跺脚震落铜鹤，暴露底舱有人。方氏父子惊慌之下凿穿船底逃走，船沉众人落水。展梦白不习水性险些溺毙，被太湖渔民\"水牛\"救起，萧飞雨亦被渔人救上船。宫伶伶因被点了睡穴，漂浮水上安然无恙，渔民误以为龙王爷显灵。太湖渔民领袖\"大鲨鱼\"与展梦白一见如故，款待众人。夜幕降临，太湖渔民举行盛大狂欢，但锣声三响后气氛骤然沉重——今夜太湖上将有变故，鲜血或染红湖水。展梦白决心留下相助，与萧飞雨并肩面对未知危机。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "我这算是什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "船家，船家，渡我过去，多给你银子。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": "char_fang_xin",
      "text": "那姓展的倒真有照命的福星，三番几次，眼见他就要倒大霉了，却偏偏总是有人出头来替他说话。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "我们此刻已上了船，饶那几个老儿奸猾，也再找不到了，只要这次无事，为父不将姓展的治得要生不生要死不死，也枉教别人称我'绝户'方辛了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "听，是谁的声音？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": "char_fang_xin",
      "text": "还有谁？正是那男不男，女不女的野丫头，幸好我们在船上，快走快走！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫老头不在，只有她和姓展的……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": "char_fang_xin",
      "text": "只有她，我们也惹不起……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "力敌不成，却能智取，凭她这样一个野丫头，和姓展的这么一个愣小子，难道还逃得过为父的掌心么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_ge",
      "text": "船家，叫船的那人，是我父子的相识，我不忍让她个女孩子叫船不应，却又不愿与她同舱，免得她难为情，你且将我父子藏到底舱下，先送她渡湖，也可多赚几文船钱。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_xin",
      "text": "爷叔，侬个人交关好。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_ge",
      "text": "千万不要说出有人在底舱，免得她个女孩难为情。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "快，快！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "那声音甜甜的女孩子对你那么关心，而我却将你拉了来，你心里不高兴，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "你本无权将我拉走。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我不拉走你，难道将你留在那里任人欺负？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "那便与你无关，你莫要以为自己得天厚些，武功高些，就可以随意定夺别人的命运，要知道人既无权随意侮辱冤枉别人，亦无权随意怜悯救助别人，只因世上有些人从不接受别人的救助、怜悯。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你不愿接受，你可有力量拒绝么？你若要拒绝人家的恶意或好意，你先就该有拒绝别人的力量，否则你不是英雄，只不过是个呆子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我这样做法，可不是为你，你也不要以为我和那些女孩子一样，是因为喜欢你才这样做的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "在下不敢。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我只是为了三阿姨，我不愿她有个不……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "三阿姨！三阿姨是你什么人？我母亲的事，自有展家人管，不用你萧家人多事。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不错，三阿姨是你母亲，你也该为她想想，你这样的武功，能复仇么？能见人么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "来历不正的武功，我却不愿去学它。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "不错，你只会逞英雄，逞骨气，表示你是男子汉大丈夫，不屑求人，但你如要想学武，难道还想人来求你么？我带你回到谷中，让你学成武功，难道有什么不好，难道对不起你？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我千方百计，都学不到武功，这小子却推三推四，他是什么东西？有哪点比我强？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": "char_fang_xin",
      "text": "我笑姓展的自作多情……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "萧丫头嘴里这么说，心里却早已爱上了姓展的，十个女人之中，有九个都喜欢脾气臭，骨头硬的男人，你笑什么？现在她已说动了姓展的，姓展的就要随她回谷练武了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贱丫头，贱丫头……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "蠢猪！你要做什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": "char_fang_xin",
      "text": "把船沉了，淹死他两个狗男女。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "说你是蠢猪，就是蠢猪，上面的人，都是活宝，弄死了他们，就不值钱了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": "char_fang_xin",
      "text": "怎么？不弄死，看他们快活！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "你看，那是什么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": "char_fang_xin",
      "text": "是什么？左右不过是个洞洞。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "等他们歇了，自那里吹些上去，只要他们嗅到一点，嘿嘿，那女的就可任凭你摆布了，再逼出白布旗的下落……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": "char_fang_xin",
      "text": "是极，是……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "禁声！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你要做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "下去休息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "下面去不得的！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你要睡就在上面睡好了，我不睡。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贱丫头，跟他一齐睡好了，假什么正经。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin",
      "speaker_name": "方辛",
      "listener": "char_fang_yi",
      "text": "你放心，原封货是你的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你跟我爹爹学武，也不致辱没了你，为什么你还像不太愿意？到了溧阳，先等一日……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "我几曾说过要跟他学武……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "怎么，说了半天，你还不愿意么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "下面一定有人！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "客人，侬那楞多心，格弗是人呀，是一只癞皮猫。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "text": "噢，原来是猫！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "方逸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这死胖婆娘，敢骂我是癞皮猫，等下非撕了她的嘴——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "text": "我最喜欢猫了，你抱来看看怎样？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "猫弗好看格，弗好看格……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "text": "闪开，我下去看看！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "格弗怪我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁？是谁？下面的那恶贼会是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "是认得侬的朋友，一个后生仔，一个老不死……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道是方家父子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "这些话以后再查，此刻先设法逃生要紧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你会不会水性？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你抓紧桌子，不要放松。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_ge",
      "text": "孩子的爹，看牢两人，叫他赔船……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "text": "你没有救他？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "客人？阿拉只救上侬一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "text": "你……他……你没有救他？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孩子的爹，孩子的爹……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_hu_yu_min",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "text": "胖大嫂你放心，牛大哥水性最好，太湖里几百条弟兄没有赶得上的，他还会出事么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_min_a",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "text": "牛大哥若会出事，我们这些人早就喂了王八了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "侬要到啥地方去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "text": "你的丈夫水性好，我的……我的他却不会水性……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不放我找他，我将你们这些人一齐杀光！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_min_b",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "不要紧，吉人自有天相，好人死不了的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_min_c",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "姑娘你等着，我们去找。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿拉弗晓得格个后生他是侬个先生……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_min_d",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看，那是什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快！快！抱他上来！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_ge",
      "text": "孩子的爹，侬好吧？",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_ge",
      "speaker_name": "牛大哥",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "text": "当然好，孩子的妈，我总算将这个客人看牢了，叫他赔船。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放开我，我对不起宫老前辈，只有一死谢他。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好朋友，你死了又有什么用？我们既然救起了你，怎么能再看着你死，没有别的话说，只有大家再一齐下去找人，先告诉我丢了的人是什么样子？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "text": "是个小女孩子，她……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_qing_yu_min",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要吵，前面好像有个人浮过来了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": "char_nian_qing_yu_min",
      "text": "看清楚些。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_qing_yu_min",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "text": "看清楚了，好像是个女孩子。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伶伶不要怕，叔叔来救你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不会水！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙王爷显圣救人，你们还不跪下来。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "兄弟，我什么都不怪你，只怪你自己不会水性，还敢下水救人。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "text": "我也不知为了什么，只是当时就情不自禁的……",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个情不自禁，兄弟们，人家这才叫做英雄汉子，救人时要的就是这份'情不自禁'的劲儿，若是救人先算一算值不值得，再想一想能不能救，这还算救人么？那简直是混账！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位姑娘还不是不会水性，就下水救人，你们只会夸男人，难道女子就没有英雄？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_min_e",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们简直是一对儿，男的是英雄汉子，女的也不差，直教人看得羡慕。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_min_f",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若不是他们这样的一对，龙王爷会显灵么？只好托他们的福，龙王爷今夜再保佑我们。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "水牛，你今日救人功劳不小，只可惜未将害人的家伙捉来，另打他们一顿。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不用了，反正……反正他们又没有害到我们。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "侬要到啥地方去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这不是赔船，只是个意思。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_min_g",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "text": "牛大嫂，你方才不是口口声声要人赔船的么，还直冲水牛瞪眼睛，此刻怎么又不好意思起来？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_min_h",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到牛大嫂居然也会脸红，居然也会不好意思，难怪龙王爷要显灵了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_sao",
      "speaker_name": "船娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死小猪，是想死快哉！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位朋友今日对展梦白之情，展某也不便言谢，反正你我俱是男儿，彼此心照。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "这样才对！展梦白，今日我大鲨鱼能认得你这样的汉子，死了也不冤枉。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "text": "但各位却一定要告诉在下，今夜太湖之上，可是有什么变故？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 485
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你既已看出，我若不要你留下，只怕难得很了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "但今晚之事，事关生死，你只要一插手其中，脱身只怕就更难得很了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "text": "无妨。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我和你一样。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能睡便睡，养精蓄锐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萧飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我们倒没有什么，只是那艘船沉了，一定要赔的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "船么，赔什么船？两位若要赔船，便是看不起我们太湖上的兄弟了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_da_ge",
      "speaker_name": "牛大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，太湖上的……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "牛大嫂，莫着急，只要今夜躲得过去，明天弟兄们还能在太湖上混，众家兄弟便为你苦上个两天，买艘新船，否则你就是有了八十条船，只怕也没有用了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "宫伶伶",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "叔叔，一个橘子是阿姨剥的，一个橘子是伶伶剥的，你两个都吃掉好么？阿姨又要我睡了，伶伶。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "醒了？睡得可好？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_sha_yu",
      "speaker_name": "大鲨鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锣声一响，狂欢开始，锣声三响，狂欢结束。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 535
    },
    {
